==Reception==
''Human Capital'' holds a 80% "Certified Fresh" rating and a [[Weighted arithmetic mean|weighted average]] of 6.81/10 on [[Rotten Tomatoes]] based on 66 reviews, with the consensus being, "Part character study, part socioeconomic fable, ''Human Capital'' offers trenchant commentary as well as absorbing drama."<ref>{{rotten-tomatoes|human_capital|Human Capital}}</ref>

